channel.title: Demonik Servers
channel.description:
If anyone has any of them. I am willing to code for them for a while, I am bored.
If you don't know me, I was the owner of RscReloaded a Demonik source with every bug\dupe fixed + Passwords Encrypted in Md5 and Salt, and everything else. I never released it though, but yeah if anyone wants help msn me.
Keithamunoz@hotmail.com.

item.title: Demonik Servers
item.dc:creator: @CodeForFame CodeForFame
item.description:
@CodeForFame wrote:

[quote=“Anc13nts253, post:4, topic:321818”][quote author=CodeForFame link=topic=418247.msg3076487#msg3076487 date=1261868869]

I shut it down, due to my other coder infecting it. But I removed it and shut it down, I was tired of paying $300 a month + a 200k session firewall. To block 50k+ Botnet attacks.

Lol @ 50k+ botnet…
[/quote]
noooob, I didn’t say I had one. I’m saying that’s what the hosting company said it might be able to block up to.

Also ‘CodeForFame’ I know who you are because we made the accounts to do stuff with anyways, why haven’t you messaged me back on msn?[/quote]
Lol, I highly doubt the hosting company can block a 50k+ botnet attack… Even with 1mBps connections that would be a 50gBps attack… Note: that’s gigabytes per second, not gigabits per second.

And what are you talking about? I don’t even know you, and I’m pretty sure I don’t have you on msn…
